<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/yemen-crisis-one-more-reason-to-re-evaluate-the-toxic-us-saudi-alliance/">Yemen Crisis: One More Reason to Re-Evaluate the Toxic US-Saudi Alliance</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">The US involvement in the Yemen crisis can be summed up in four words: allegiance to Saudi Arabia.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/medea-benjamin/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Medea Benjamin</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.codepink.org/yemen_crisis' itemprop='url'>PINKtank</a></span></dd>
